---
import PageLayout from "../layouts/PageLayout.astro";
---

<PageLayout
  title="The Challenge"
  heroTitle="Chapter One: To Conquer the Pyrenees"
  heroSubtitle="A complete coast-to-coast traverse of one of Europe's most challenging mountain ranges. Self-supported. Side by side."
  heroTitleKey="theChallenge.heroTitle"
  heroSubtitleKey="theChallenge.heroSubtitle"
>
  <!-- Stats -->
  <section class="border-b border-stone-800">
    <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10 py-16">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="border-l-2 border-amber-500/40 pl-4">
          <p class="font-display text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-stone-100">
            ~12
          </p>
          <p
            class="text-stone-500 text-sm mt-1 font-body"
            data-i18n="stats.totalDays"
          >
            Total Days
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-amber-500/40 pl-4">
          <p class="font-display text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-stone-100">
            ~1,000
          </p>
          <p
            class="text-stone-500 text-sm mt-1 font-body"
            data-i18n="stats.kilometres"
          >
            Kilometres
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-amber-500/40 pl-4">
          <p class="font-display text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-stone-100">
            ~22,000
          </p>
          <p
            class="text-stone-500 text-sm mt-1 font-body"
            data-i18n="stats.metresOfClimbing"
          >
            Metres of Climbing
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-amber-500/40 pl-4">
          <p class="font-display text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-amber-400">
            ~2.5×
          </p>
          <p
            class="text-stone-500 text-sm mt-1 font-body"
            data-i18n="stats.heightOfEverest"
          >
            The Height of Everest
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Challenge Description -->
  <section>
    <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10 py-24 lg:py-40">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p
          class="text-stone-300 text-xl leading-relaxed font-body"
          data-i18n="theChallenge.introDesc"
        >
          This is more than a bike ride; it's the next chapter in our shared
          story. A testament to Edurne's unwavering support through every step
          of my GBS journey, this is our challenge — a complete coast-to-coast
          traverse of one of the Europe's most challenging mountain ranges.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Route sections -->
      <div class="mt-20 space-y-16">
        <!-- Shared Journey -->
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
          <div class="lg:col-span-4">
            <span
              class="text-amber-500 font-body text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase"
              data-i18n="theChallenge.styleTag">The Style</span
            >
            <h2
              class="font-display text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-stone-100 mt-3"
              data-i18n="theChallenge.styleTitle"
            >
              A Shared Journey
            </h2>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-8">
            <p
              class="text-stone-400 text-lg leading-relaxed font-body"
              data-i18n="theChallenge.styleDesc1"
            >
              This challenge is a journey we will undertake as a team,
              side-by-side. We'll be riding in a self-supported bikepacking
              style, carrying all our own equipment and relying on the kindness
              of the community we meet along the way.
            </p>
            <p
              class="text-stone-500 text-lg leading-relaxed font-body mt-4"
              data-i18n="theChallenge.styleDesc2"
            >
              We would be honored and motivated to have local riders join us for
              a few kilometers or to share the effort on a classic mountain
              pass. This journey is about community, and we welcome anyone who
              wants to be a part of it.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="h-px bg-stone-800"></div>

        <!-- 01 The Start -->
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
          <div class="lg:col-span-4">
            <div class="bg-stone-900 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-stone-800">
              <span
                class="text-amber-500/50 font-display text-4xl font-bold"
                data-i18n="theChallenge.theStartNum">01</span
              >
              <h3
                class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-stone-100 mt-2"
                data-i18n="theChallenge.theStartTitle"
              >
                The Start
              </h3>
              <div class="mt-4 space-y-2">
                <div class="flex justify-between text-sm font-body">
                  <span
                    class="text-stone-500"
                    data-i18n="theChallenge.direction">Direction</span
                  >
                  <span
                    class="text-stone-300"
                    data-i18n="theChallenge.theStartDirection"
                    >Mediterranean → Atlantic</span
                  >
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between text-sm font-body">
                  <span class="text-stone-500" data-i18n="theChallenge.distance"
                    >Distance</span
                  >
                  <span
                    class="text-stone-300"
                    data-i18n="theChallenge.theStartDistance">~400km</span
                  >
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between text-sm font-body">
                  <span
                    class="text-stone-500"
                    data-i18n="theChallenge.elevationGain">Elevation Gain</span
                  >
                  <span
                    class="text-stone-300"
                    data-i18n="theChallenge.theStartElevationGain">~8000m</span
                  >
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between text-sm font-body">
                  <span class="text-stone-500" data-i18n="theChallenge.terrain"
                    >Terrain</span
                  >
                  <span
                    class="text-stone-300"
                    data-i18n="theChallenge.theStartTerrain"
                    >High cols, steep gradients</span
                  >
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-8 flex items-center">
            <div>
              <p
                class="text-stone-400 text-lg leading-relaxed font-body"
                data-i18n="theChallenge.theStartDesc"
              >
                East from the Basque coast, battling the legendary cols of the
                French Pyrenees. Aubisque, Tourmalet, Aspin — names that echo
                through cycling history. Each summit is a victory over both
                mountain and the limitations GBS tried to impose. The French
                side is characterised by steep, dramatic climbs and deep,
                verdant valleys that funnel you toward the next great challenge.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="h-px bg-stone-800"></div>

        <!-- 02 The Climbing -->
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
          <div class="lg:col-span-4">
            <div class="bg-stone-900 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-stone-800">
              <span
                class="text-amber-500/50 font-display text-4xl font-bold"
                data-i18n="theChallenge.theClimbingNum">02</span
              >
              <h3
                class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-stone-100 mt-2"
                data-i18n="theChallenge.theClimbingTitle"
              >
                The Climbing
              </h3>
              <div class="mt-4 space-y-2">
                <div class="flex justify-between text-sm font-body">
                  <span
                    class="text-stone-500"
                    data-i18n="theChallenge.direction">Direction</span
                  >
                  <span
                    class="text-stone-300"
                    data-i18n="theChallenge.theClimbingDirection"
                    >Spain → France → Spain</span
                  >
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between text-sm font-body">
                  <span class="text-stone-500" data-i18n="theChallenge.theClimbingDistance"
                    >Distance</span
                  >
                  <span
                    class="text-stone-300"
                    data-i18n="theChallenge.theClimbingDistance">~200km</span
                  >
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between text-sm font-body">
                  <span
                    class="text-stone-500"
                    data-i18n="theChallenge.theClimbingElevationGain">Elevation Gain</span
                  >
                  <span
                    class="text-stone-300"
                    data-i18n="theChallenge.theClimbingElevationGain">~7000m</span
                  >
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between text-sm font-body">
                  <span class="text-stone-500" data-i18n="theChallenge.theClimbingTerrain"
                    >Terrain</span
                  >
                  <span
                    class="text-stone-300"
                    data-i18n="theChallenge.theClimbingTerrain"
                    >Long, remote climbs</span
                  >
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-8 flex items-center">
            <div>
              <p
                class="text-stone-400 text-lg leading-relaxed font-body"
                data-i18n="theChallenge.theClimbingDesc"
              >
                After reaching the Mediterranean, the journey turns west for the
                long road home. This is a test of endurance and heart, a deep
                dive into the Spanish side of the mountains. Our route will
                focus on the long, remote, and beautiful roads of Catalunya,
                Aragón, and finally, Navarra. The climbs are less steep but just
                as relentless, demanding a different kind of strength for the
                journey back to the Atlantic.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="h-px bg-stone-800"></div>

        <!-- 03 The Finish -->
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
          <div class="lg:col-span-4">
            <div class="bg-stone-900 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-stone-800">
              <span
                class="text-amber-500/50 font-display text-4xl font-bold"
                data-i18n="theChallenge.theFinishNum">03</span
              >
              <h3
                class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-stone-100 mt-2"
                data-i18n="theChallenge.theFinishTitle"
              >
                The Finish
              </h3>
              <div class="mt-4 space-y-2">
                <div class="flex justify-between text-sm font-body">
                  <span
                    class="text-stone-500"
                    data-i18n="theChallenge.direction">Direction</span
                  >
                  <span
                    class="text-stone-300"
                    data-i18n="theChallenge.theFinishDirection"
                    >Spain → Atlantic Coast</span
                  >
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between text-sm font-body">
                  <span class="text-stone-500" data-i18n="theChallenge.distance"
                    >Distance</span
                  >
                  <span
                    class="text-stone-300"
                    data-i18n="theChallenge.theFinishDistance">~300km</span
                  >
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between text-sm font-body">
                  <span
                    class="text-stone-500"
                    data-i18n="theChallenge.elevationGain">Elevation Gain</span
                  >
                  <span
                    class="text-stone-300"
                    data-i18n="theChallenge.theFinishElevationGain">~5000m</span
                  >
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between text-sm font-body">
                  <span class="text-stone-500" data-i18n="theChallenge.terrain"
                    >Terrain</span
                  >
                  <span
                    class="text-stone-300"
                    data-i18n="theChallenge.theFinishTerrain"
                    >Rolling hills, coastal roads</span
                  >
                </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-8 flex items-center">
            <div>
              <p
                class="text-stone-400 text-lg leading-relaxed font-body"
                data-i18n="theChallenge.theFinishDesc"
              >
                This will be some description of finally reaching the Atlantic coast, the emotions of completing the challenge, and the final push to the finish line. The terrain will be less mountainous but still demanding, with rolling hills and coastal roads that test the legs after weeks in the mountains.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="h-px bg-stone-800"></div>

        <!-- 04 The Homecoming -->
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
          <div class="lg:col-span-4">
            <div class="bg-stone-900 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-stone-800">
              <span
                class="text-amber-500/50 font-display text-4xl font-bold"
                data-i18n="theChallenge.theHomecomingNum">04</span
              >
              <h3
                class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-stone-100 mt-2"
                data-i18n="theChallenge.theHomecomingTitle"
              >
                The Homecoming
              </h3>
              <div class="mt-4 space-y-2">
                <div class="flex justify-between text-sm font-body">
                  <span
                    class="text-stone-500"
                    data-i18n="theChallenge.direction">Direction</span
                  >
                  <span
                    class="text-stone-300"
                    data-i18n="theChallenge.theHomecomingDirection"
                    >Hondarribia → Pamplona</span
                  >
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between text-sm font-body">
                  <span class="text-stone-500" data-i18n="theChallenge.theHomecomingDistance"
                    >Distance</span
                  >
                  <span
                    class="text-stone-300"
                    data-i18n="theChallenge.theHomecomingDistance">~100km</span
                  >
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between text-sm font-body">
                  <span
                    class="text-stone-500"
                    data-i18n="theChallenge.theHomecomingElevationGain">Elevation Gain</span
                  >
                  <span
                    class="text-stone-300"
                    data-i18n="theChallenge.theHomecomingElevationGain">~2000m</span
                  >
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between text-sm font-body">
                  <span class="text-stone-500" data-i18n="theChallenge.theHomecomingTerrain"
                    >Terrain</span
                  >
                  <span
                    class="text-stone-300"
                    data-i18n="theChallenge.theHomecomingTerrain"
                    >Gentle valleys, celebration</span
                  >
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-8 flex items-center">
            <div>
              <p
                class="text-stone-400 text-lg leading-relaxed font-body"
                data-i18n="theChallenge.theHomecomingDesc"
              >
                This will be some description about the final stage, the homecoming, the celebration, the emotions of returning to Pamplona after conquering the Pyrenees. It will be a mix of relief, joy, and reflection on the journey that has been both a physical and emotional challenge.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="mt-24 text-center">
        <a
          href="/donate"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-amber-500 text-stone-950 px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-body font-bold hover:bg-amber-400 transition-colors"
        >
          <span data-i18n="theChallenge.supportChallenge"
            >Support This Challenge</span
          >
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
